Read UCINET's .dl files

Source: R/read_ucinet.R
read_ucinet.Rd

Read UCINET's .dl files

read_ucinet(path, directed = NULL)

Arguments

path

Path to file or URL.

Value

A network_dataset object.

Examples

library(snatools)

"http://vlado.fmf.uni-lj.si/pub/networks/data/ucinet/sampson.dat" %>%
  read_ucinet()
